        PERFORM 700-DISPLAY-MESSAGE
        MOVE "3. Learn a new skill" TO MESSAGE-BUFFER
        PERFORM 700-DISPLAY-MESSAGE
        MOVE "4. View My Pending Connection Requests" TO MESSAGE-BUFFER
